<headline>Heat Advisory issued June 26 at 7:54PM MDT until June 27 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Albuquerque</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT FROM NOON TO 8 PM MDT TUESDAY...
* WHAT...Temperatures up to 105 expected.
* WHERE...Southwest Chaves County.
* WHEN...From Noon to 8 PM MDT Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
